<template>
<v-container>
  <v-row
  class="pt-9"
  justify="center">
    <v-img
    src="../assets/snake.png"
    max-width="300"
    height="300"
    >
    </v-img>
  </v-row>
  <v-container class="mt-9">
    <v-row justify="center">
      <v-btn
      class="mr-5"
      color="primary"
      elevation="10"
      @click="getUsers"
      >
        SCORES
      </v-btn>
      <UserName/>
    </v-row>
  </v-container>
</v-container>
</template>
<script>
import axios from "axios";
import UserName from "../components/UserName"
export default {
  name: "get-users",
  components: {
    UserName,
  },
  data() {
    return {
      users: []
    };
  },
  methods: {
    getUsers: async function () {
      await axios.get('http://localhost:8000/users')
        .then(res => {
          this.users = res.data;
          console.log(this.users);
        })
        .catch(err => {
          console.log(err);
        });
    }
  }
}
</script>
<style scoped>
</style>
